{"tid":205434,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[人唔笑  狗都吠] [扮盲] 青山云：無人寫得出港獨理論  《民族論》唔算","createTime":"2017-04-17T18:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T03:22:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8f4bf757ee459e22a5d4e3e4a466f199d55862","tid":205434,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T18:42:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155124293342225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155124293342225&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0d1b1274\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155124293342225</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：我都好想世代交替，將政治理論家的位置交給年輕人，親自開文化沙龍講座，傾囊相授，無遮擋地廣傳知識及經驗，自己休息下，做華夏宗教研究，神道設教。不過，等了五年，青年人都無寫出港獨理論，反而不斷徵引我在《香港城邦論》的實然主權來應付傳媒，又去英國查看當年香港的舊檔案，這些我在《香港城邦論》系列寫過，他們去重新發明車輪（re-inventing the wheel），用年齡訴求來盜竊我的支持者。<br />\n<br />\n我在上世紀八十年代，二十幾歲的時候，已經在香港政壇成為獨當一面的政治理論家。爆發六四屠殺的時候，我已經在香港《解放月刊》提出香港自治理論（雜誌的刊登版本曾經貼出來及重新打字在《熱血時報》刊載）。<br />\n<br />\n年齡？後生仔大嗮？係ga。陳雲後生的時候，確實是大嗮ga，獨當一面，不借用人家理論、不盜竊人家的支持者地盤，完全自創天下，當年的老前輩都樂意提攜我，將學問傾囊相授。現在的後生仔，學下囉。"},{"pid":"5b79bc3e5a1200d062f02db023c36ef97f3e362f","tid":205434,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T18:46:07.000Z","msg":"都OK好笑架佢<br />\n<br />\n同共產黨LOGIC一樣：香港人都係支那籍, BNO唔算國籍<br />\n<br />\n云伯：無人寫得出港獨理論, 《民族論》唔算<br />\n<br />\n《獨立論》？提都唔敢提啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc2d4336d385f778764e678f9152b28fc20880f","tid":205434,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T18:47:37.000Z","msg":"民族論作者屌柒陳云根：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iHor3PqdL30#t=12m12s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiHor3PqdL30%23t%3D12m12s&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=346a4711\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iHor3PqdL30#t=12m12s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89a13bca06fb248d30e89ace642b034fb5f32c0","tid":205434,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"鴕鳥政策（ostrich policy）<br />\n<br />\n我陳云根係天下無敵架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/head+in+sand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F06%2Fhead%2Bin%2Bsand.jpg&h=7637c770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}